description: [``botocore``] New feature: Updated EC2 API to support faster launching for Windows images. Optimized images are pre-provisioned, using snapshots to launch instances up to 65% faster.
[``botocore``] Adds support for new Compute Optimizer capability that makes it easier for customers to optimize their EC2 instances by leveraging multiple CPU architectures.
[``botocore``] This release adds FailureType in the response of DescribeAnomalyDetector.
[``botocore``] This SDK release adds support for specifying a Bucket Owner for an S3 location.
